text: Mynämäki is a municipality in Southwest Finland, Finland. As of January 2014 about 7950 people lived there. Neighbouring municipalities are Aura, Eura, Laitila, Masku, Nousiainen, Pöytyä, Rusko, Taivassalo, Turku and Vehmaa. Most people speak Finnish. == Other websites == * Mynämäki website Category:Municipalities of Southwest Finland
